                        <li><strong>Images are distorted:</strong> Use object-contain (shows full image) or object-cover (fills space) with aspect-square to prevent stretching.</li>
                        <li><strong>Cards have different heights:</strong> Apply aspect-square to the image container, not the entire card. Only the image section should be square.</li>
                        <li><strong>IDs show as "1" instead of "001":</strong> Use .ToString("D3") with the integer ID, not the string from the API. Parse the ID first: int.Parse(lastSegment).</li>
